shapeMap
Class ShapeMapModel

java.lang.Object
  shapeMap.ShapeMapModel

public class ShapeMapModel
extends java.lang.Object

This class stores the data necessary to reconstruct a shape map - the model of the shape map. This includes only a list of shapes. This class is a Java Bean, so can be written to an XML file using Java's XMLEncoder

Author:
Curran Kelleher
